data.description:
Single Story home with 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms and 3 car garage just over 3000 sq.ft! Spacious backyard with pool and spa! 
Open concept home with warm paint tones throughout the house. Separate Master's bedroom, formal dining room, formal living room with dual fireplace and private office that's perfect for working from home. Master's  bath  comes with jacuzzi tub, separate vanities and walk in closet. Large kitchen with ample cabinet space. Open kitchen island perfect for entertaining and cooking meals.  Easy access to 215 Freeway, close to Aliante Station and near VA Hospital. Close to shopping and dining.
